<%#
# DatePicker Show Partial

This partial renders a date to be displayed
on a resource's show page.

By default, the attribute is rendered as string
with the %b %d, %Y format, e.g. `Oct 28, 2016`

## Local variables:

- `field`:
  An instance of DateTime.
%>

